					<li>Attempt to gain unauthorized access to any part of the Service</li>
					<li>Use the Service to transmit harmful, offensive, or fraudulent content</li>
					<li>Use the Service for money laundering or other financial crimes</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>6. Funds and Contributions</h2>
				<ul>
					<li>Fund creators are responsible for the accurate description and management of their funds.</li>
					<li>Contributions made through the Service are subject to processing by third-party payment providers.</li>
					<li>Refund policies for contributions are determined by the fund creator and applicable law.</li>
					<li>We are not responsible for disputes between fund participants.</li>
				</ul>

				<h2>7. Fees and Payments</h2>
				<p>
					Certain features of the Service may require payment. All fees are described within the application. Payment processing is handled by third-party providers, and their terms also apply to transactions made through the Service.
				</p>

				<h2>8. Intellectual Property</h2>
				<p>
					The Service, including its design, features, and content, is owned by Spread the Fund and is protected by intellectual property laws. You may not reproduce, distribute, or create derivative works of the Service without our written permission.
				</p>

